    <!-- Edit Wizard -->
    <string name="edit_wizard_text">Welcome to edit player screen! Here you can set a name for your
        player profile, pick a color for the life counter, and select images for the background.
    </string>
    <string name="edit_wizard_text_2">If you decide to customize your back ground (you should it\'s
        awesome!), in the next screen you will be asked to pick a tall and a large picture. The tall
        one will be used in portrait mode, and the large in landscape. You can chose between loading
        an image directly, or crop it to fit the aspect ratio.
    </string>
    <string name="edit_wizard_text_3">From there, you can simply apply changes (it won\'t save
        anything), or save your edited profile. Note that profiles are stored by name so if you
        change the name it will create a new profile. You can also load and edit profiles here. Have
        fun!
    </string>


